      "locked": false,
      "text": "Running Example\nThe example machine uses four 3.0 Nm NEMA 23\nclosed-loop steppers: X, Z, and two\nsynchronized Y gantry motors driven by encoder\ndrives from a 6-axis FluidNC controller.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
