      "text": "Controller Core Job\nA CNC controller interprets commands,\nplans coordinated motion, emits drive\ncommands, watches inputs, and enforces\nmachine state.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-107b2883c63d",
      "originalText": "Controller Core Job\nA CNC controller interprets commands, plans coordinated motion, emits drive commands, watches inputs, and enforces machine state.",
