      "text": "Embedded Step-Dir\nFirmware controllers such as FluidNC are compact and\npractical for routers, lasers, plasma tables, and\nsmall machines that use step/dir drives.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
