      "text": "External Motion Card\nA PC user interface can delegate real-time motion to\nan Ethernet, USB, or PCI motion card that owns pulse\ntiming or fieldbus cycles.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-4d2bad3d52dc",
      "originalText": "External Motion Card\nA PC user interface can delegate real-time motion to an Ethernet, USB, or PCI motion card that owns pulse timing or fieldbus cycles.",
