      "text": "Robot Controller\nRobotics controllers solve multi-axis kinematics,\ncoordinated servo loops, safe zones, and\nteach-pendant workflows rather than pure Cartesian\nG-code motion.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-6e4d61f916f2",
      "originalText": "Robot Controller\nRobotics controllers solve multi-axis kinematics, coordinated servo loops, safe zones, and teach-pendant workflows rather than pure Cartesian G-code motion.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "customData": {
        "node_id": "robot-controller"
      }
    },
