      "text": "Dual Y Gantry\nThe example machine uses two closed-loop Y\nmotors because a wide gantry needs torque on\nboth sides and must avoid racking.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-668db31ef287",
      "originalText": "Dual Y Gantry\nThe example machine uses two closed-loop Y motors because a wide gantry needs torque on both sides and must avoid racking.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "customData": {
        "node_id": "dual-y-gantry"
      }
    },
