      "text": "Braking Energy\nDecelerating axes and spindles return energy to the\nDC bus, which may require braking resistors,\nregenerative drives, or conservative decel limits.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-fe516152ffb0",
