      "text": "Cabinet Power Chain\nThe cabinet should have a legible chain from\nmains entry to disconnect, fusing,\nfiltering, contactors, supplies, drives, and\nloads.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-85f8b10431f7",
      "originalText": "Cabinet Power Chain\nThe cabinet should have a legible chain from mains entry to disconnect, fusing, filtering, contactors, supplies, drives, and loads.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "customData": {
        "node_id": "cabinet-power-chain"
      }
    },
