      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-9e20d3f759c4",
      "originalText": "Contactor Strategy\nContactors can remove drive or spindle power, but drive-integrated safety such as STO is often a cleaner motion-safety mechanism.",
