      "text": "Grounding And Bonding\nGrounding is for fault current and reference\nstability; shielding is for noise control;\nmixing those mental models causes cabinet\nproblems.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
