      "text": "Shielding And Routing\nRoute high-energy switching cables away from\nlow-level signals, and terminate shields\ndeliberately instead of leaving them\ndecorative.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-e09c35ea6cae",
      "originalText": "Shielding And Routing\nRoute high-energy switching cables away from low-level signals, and terminate shields deliberately instead of leaving them decorative.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "customData": {
        "node_id": "shielding-and-routing"
      }
    },
