      "text": "Motor Cables\nMotor phase cables carry fast switching currents and\nshould be shielded, mechanically protected, and\nseparated from encoder and sensor wiring.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-4b9a980fd368",
