      "text": "Encoder Cables\nEncoder wiring needs twisted pairs, shield\ncontinuity, correct termination, and separation from\nVFD, plasma, laser, and motor power wiring.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
