      "text": "VFD Cables\nSpindle VFD output cables are a major EMI source and\nshould use VFD-rated shielded cable, proper shield\ntermination, and routing discipline.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-8cc15090ef6e",
      "originalText": "VFD Cables\nSpindle VFD output cables are a major EMI source and should use VFD-rated shielded cable, proper shield termination, and routing discipline.",
