      "text": "Debounce And Filtering\nLimit switches, probes, and E-stop feedback need\nhardware and software filtering chosen so noise is\nignored but real events are not delayed dangerously.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-84796ce4bdba",
      "originalText": "Debounce And Filtering\nLimit switches, probes, and E-stop feedback need hardware and software filtering chosen so noise is ignored but real events are not delayed dangerously.",
