      "text": "Software Stop Trap\nA feed hold, pause button, or sender\ndisconnect is operational control; it is not a\nsubstitute for a rated emergency stop chain.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-c215292b7700",
      "originalText": "Software Stop Trap\nA feed hold, pause button, or sender disconnect is operational control; it is not a substitute for a rated emergency stop chain.",
