      "text": "Industrial Safety\nIndustrial safety starts with risk assessment,\nthen assigns rated hardware and validation\nevidence to each hazard instead of treating\nsafety as normal control logic.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-432b73963b21",
      "originalText": "Industrial Safety\nIndustrial safety starts with risk assessment, then assigns rated hardware and validation evidence to each hazard instead of treating safety as normal control logic.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "customData": {
        "node_id": "industrial-safety"
      }
    },
