      "text": "Fieldbus Conversion\nA fieldbus upgrade moves command, feedback,\ndiagnostics, and drive state into a\ndeterministic network and usually changes the\ncontroller class.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15.0,
      "containerId": "node-d58a9d042607",
      "originalText": "Fieldbus Conversion\nA fieldbus upgrade moves command, feedback, diagnostics, and drive state into a deterministic network and usually changes the controller class.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "customData": {
        "node_id": "fieldbus-conversion"
      }
    },
